[Super Street Fighter 2 Turbo Codes\Crazy Hit & Knockdown Mechanics]
author=BigBossman
description=This will cause Player 1 to drift toward Player 2 & Player 2 toward Player 1 if they should get hit, block an attack, or get thrown. If Player 1 & Player 2 switch sides, it has the opposite effect. This is a good way to keep racking up hits & easily inflict dizziness. Some attacks won't knock your opponent down. Sometimes your character may even seem to teleport while performing an attack.
patch=1,EE,1084C1B2,extended,00000001
patch=1,EE,1084C5B2,extended,00000000

